            <p>Hey there,<br /><br /><br />My name is Karan Mahajan.</p>
<p>I have created the Weather App to provide you with accurate and up-to-date weather information for any location around the globe.</p>
<h4>Features</h4>
<ul>
<li><strong>Real-Time Weather Updates:</strong> Get current weather conditions including temperature, humidity, and wind speed.</li>
<li><strong>Location Search:</strong> Easily search for weather information by city or geographic coordinates.</li>
<li><strong>User-Friendly Interface:</strong> Enjoy a clean, intuitive design that makes it simple to find the weather data you need.</li>
<li><strong>Responsive Design:</strong> The app works seamlessly on both desktop and mobile devices, ensuring you have access to weather updates wherever you go.</li>
</ul>
<h4>Technology Stack</h4>
<p>The Weather App is built using the following technologies:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Node.js:</strong> A powerful JavaScript runtime for building fast and scalable network applications.</li>
<li><strong>Express.js:</strong> A minimal and flexible Node.js web application framework that provides a robust set of features for web and mobile applications.</li>
<li><strong>Handlebars:</strong> A simple templating language that allows you to create semantic templates effectively.</li>
<li><strong>HTML/CSS:</strong> The backbone of the user interface, providing structure and style to the app.</li>
<li><strong>JavaScript:</strong> For dynamic content and interactive features.</li>
<li><strong>API Integration:</strong> Integration with reliable weather APIs to fetch accurate weather data.</li>
</ul>
<h4>Mission</h4>
<p>The aim is to provide users with a reliable and easy-to-use weather forecasting tool that helps them make informed decisions based on current weather conditions. The commitment is to continually improve the app by adding new features and ensuring the highest accuracy of the weather data provided.</p>
